# Baseeth

Baseeth is a developer-oriented repository focused on
Ethereum Layer 2 architecture with hands-on exploration
of the Base network built on the OP Stack.

## Scope
- Ethereum L1 fundamentals
- Layer 2 rollups and scaling
- Base network internals
- OP Stack concepts
- Smart contract development (Solidity)

## Repository Layout
- Base/   → Base network research and tooling
- Base3/  → Web3 experiments on Base
- Chain/  → Blockchain core concepts
- L2/     → Layer
